programme.title: The Kiss Addict

programme.title: Man On The Edge

programme.title: Legally Declared Dead

programme.title: The Tag-Along: Devil Fish

programme.title: The Narrow Road

programme.title: Acting Out Of Love

programme.title: Hello Mr. Billionaire

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon 2020
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. How does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kong's legendary detective?

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: An urban sketcher suffering from ALS wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. Then, he asks his old classmate to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day.

programme.title: Flashover

programme.title: Men On The Dragon

programme.title: Caught In Time

programme.title: Touch Of The Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh.

Shaolin Prince

programme.title: Songfest

programme.title: Tales Of A Eunuch

programme.title: Return Of The Crazy Bumpkins

programme.title: Trilogy Of Swordsmanship
programme.desc: A trilogy of tales featuring clever courtesans, battling brigands and a virginal innocent.

programme.title: Diau Charn

programme.title: Return Of The Sentimental...

programme.title: The Snake Prince

programme.title: Pursuit Of Vengeance

programme.title: The Female Prince

programme.title: The Tigress Of Shaolin

programme.title: Return Of The Dead

programme.title: Top Of The Top Spc. 11th Anniv.
The Thundering Sword

programme.title: Woman Of The Night

programme.title: The Lady Professional

programme.title: The Kingdom And The Beauty

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
